W. H. Bethea, as Tax Assessor of Taylor County, Plaintiff in Error, v. State ex rel. Burton Swartz Cypress Co., Defendant in Error. A Writ of Error to a Judgment of the Circuit Court within and for the County of Taylor. Yam 0. Swearmgen, Attorney General, for Plaintiff in Error; W. B. Dams, for Defendant in Error.

Writ of Error dimissed on motion of the Attorney General.
